# VHS Tape: Haiphen Network — protocol trace with anomaly report
# Zoomed 640×360 @ 20px — single focused command

Output "docs/assets/demos/cli-network.gif"

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 20
Set Width 640
Set Height 360
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 12
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Hide
Type `export PATH="DEMO_DIR:$PATH" PS1='$ '`
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Show

Type "haiphen network trace --protocol modbus"
Enter
Sleep 2.5s

Sleep 3s
